{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As a resident of PHSSB, a report can be made following the steps below:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Go to https://aduanku.my\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Click on the \u8220"Report a problem\u8221" link and enter the nearest street to PPR Kota Damansara; which is \u8220"Jalan Pekaka 8/1\u8221":\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi0 {\cf1 [image: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leowmjw/my-articles/master/SINARPROJECT/OPENSPENDING/ADUANKU/assets/Aduanku_Report_Issue_Start.png]\cf0}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Fill in all the necessary information as show below:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi0 {\cf1 [image: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leowmjw/my-articles/master/SINARPROJECT/OPENSPENDING/ADUANKU/assets/Aduanku_Reporting_By_Resident.png]\cf0}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab As a resident, if it is a sensitive matter; contact your resource person {\b Peng Lim} via alternative channel (on Whatsapp). There should be a shared email account that can be used in this case.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As we can see in the example below; this is what PHSSB will see when a report is made:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 ----------\line
\line
Tracking Id: 857\line
\line
Name: Sinar Project\line
\line
Email: leow+aduanku@sinarproject.org\line
\line
Phone: 0162332450\line
\line
Category: Lampu Jalan\line
\line
Subject: Test PPR Report Visibility in Dashboard\line
\line
Details: Test;ignore\line
\line
Latitude: 3.176146\line
\line
Longitude: 101.577803\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So as long as the reporter either gets the resource person (e.g Peng Lim) to report on their behalf; or use a throw away email; PHSSB will not be able to identify the reporter.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b REMEMBER:} The {\b phone number} and {\b name} field is {\b OPTIONAL} In order to obfuscate the report; use a shared email, the JMB should make contact only via email\par}
